title: 2010.05.29-F1.07.Turkey.Qualifying.BBC1_UK [TDMK1]
description:
2010.05.29-F1.07.Turkey.Qualifying.BBC1_UK-TDMK1.m4v

Jake Humphrey is joined by Eddie Jordan and David Coulthard for live coverage of the session at Istanbul Park, as the drivers contest grid positions for the seventh race of the season. Jenson Button recorded his sixth victory of the campaign when taking the chequered flag here in 2009, triumphing ahead of Mark Webber after starting second on the grid behind eventual third-place finisher Sebastian Vettel. Commentary by Jonathan Legard and Martin Brundle.

Now encoded as 'MP4 All Play'... As a departure from the DivX files which I have uploaded in the past, I've made the decision to get with the 21st century & start encoding with the following specs this year;

MP4 - 640x352 - 800Kb/s H264 Video - 44.1KHz/128Kbps Stereo AAC Audio

My belief is this is the best all round setup, and hopefully you will agree!

This video will play on a computer with VLC, XBMC, XBox360, PS3, all iPhones - enjoy the show... :)
